title: Best REAL Hip-Hop and Rap Songs Of June 2013 [2-Disc]
description:
The latest monthly compilation from Real HipHopHead. A lot of dope and slept-on joints. The best Hip-Hop that dropped in this past month of May 2013. 2 Discs, 44 total tracks. Enjoy.

Artists featured include: Freddie Gibbs, Slum Village, Jay Electronica, Qwel and Maker, Statik Selektah, Killer Mike & El-P, Wu-Tang Clan, J. Cole, Nas, Shad, Prodigy & Alchemist, Quasimoto and more.
